OL,5, Fruit flavours may be banned and extra 
OL,6, taxes applied to e-cigarettes, in a    
OL,7, crackdown on vaping aimed at children. 
OL,9,FLegislation to allow tighter           
OL,10,Frestrictions was promised in the King's
OL,11,FSpeech, earlier on Tuesday.            
OL,13,FThe move, which could apply to the     
OL,14,Fwhole of the UK, could also see vapes  
OL,15,Fhaving to be hidden from view in shops 
OL,16,Fand plain packaging introduced.        
OL,18,FAnd, as promised last month, ministers 
OL,19,Fwill also be looking to raise the age  
OL,20,Fof sale for smoking.                   
